Package: logrotate
Section: utils
Architecture: ARCH
Priority: important
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, fcron
Description: tool used to simplify the administration of log files 
 This package provide logrotate, a tool used to simplify 
 the administration of log files.
 .
 Logrotate allows for the automatic rotation compression, 
 removal and mailing of log files. Logrotate can be set 
 to handle a log file daily, weekly, monthly or when the 
 log file gets to a certain size.

Package: logrotate-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Priority: optional
Depends: logrotate (= ${binary:Version})
Recommends: man-db
Description: documentation for logrotate
 This package provides the manual page for logrotate.
